sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_061_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Clear Authorization Data in Authorization Cache

    CS->>CP: 1. ClearCache.req
    CP-->>CS: 2. ClearCache.conf (status=Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    Note over CP,CS: Expected: Charge Point Authorization Cache is cleared
